    "\n",
    "### What GreenTensor Does\n",
    "\n",
    "GreenTensor is the first middleware platform that simultaneously:\n",
    "- **Reduces GPU compute costs** via mixed precision, cuDNN, and batch optimization\n",
    "- **Measures carbon and water impact** per AI workload with real hardware counters\n",
    "- **Detects ML-specific cyberattacks** (cryptominers, model theft, backdoors)\n",
    "- **Generates regulatory ESG reports** aligned with GHG Protocol, SEC, and EU CSRD\n",
    "- **Schedules jobs for the cleanest grid window** using real-time carbon intensity data\n",
    "\n",
    "All from a **single Python context manager** around your existing training code.\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Training GPT-4 consumed ~700,000 liters of fresh water and emitted ~500 tonnes of CO2.\n",
    "Global AI compute demand doubles every 6 months.\n",
    "By 2030, AI is projected to consume 3-4% of global electricity.\n",
    "```\n"
